text: Vicente Iturat Gil (22 August 1928 – 18 August 2017) was a Spanish cyclist. He won the Points classification in the 1957 Vuelta a España. He was born in Alcalà de Xivert, Spain. Iturat died on 18 August 2017 in Vilanova i la Geltrú, Spain at the age of 88. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Spanish cyclists
